  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK313">
<l>ceyyāmal ceṟṟārkku miṉṉāta ceytapi</l>
<l>ṉuyyā viḻuman tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If an ascetic inflict suffering even on those who hate him, when he has not done them any evil, it will afterwards give him irretrievable sorrow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
